{"type": "article", "id": 20980, "title": "湖海餐具组", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-20T07:40:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 78, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122314SQYapAJbnMTWrF8c.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是造作新推的湖海餐具组，在碗和盘子的边缘有小的波纹。它是以组合的形式售卖，设计时也考虑到了相互搭配，粉色、蓝色、墨绿色搭配在其中，有清新自然的水墨效果。而每一个组合里都有一个完全纯色的碗或盘子，让颜色有了沉淀。两组分别售价 102 元和 152 元，<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300087\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150709RtOSIUju1N06PEva.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"368\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.34074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072615070930FBN7wx9rphzaAD.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"375\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.34722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150710rKV6zEIUgHlxGqXa.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"460\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.42592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150710e8swYuEmKqNTFZ9n.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}